                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/8808" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">FAM-1346</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">1742 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">“税”到渠成，“筹”以破局——非上市公司股权激励之个税筹划</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">&quot;When taxes flow smoothly, planning breaks the deadlock&quot; —— Tax Planning for Individual Income Tax in Equity Incentives for Non-Listed Companies</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">陈祖英，陈俊文，曾馨，徐玥</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">福建农林大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">福建智行科技信息技术有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">其他</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">财务资产部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">15 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">决策型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">股权激励；个人所得税；递延纳税政策；非上市公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Equity incentives; Personal income tax; Deferred tax policy; Non-listed companies</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">高新技术企业对核心人才有着极高的依赖度。为了稳定并激发这些人才的潜力，实施股权激励成为企业发展壮大不可或缺的战略选择。然而，从激励效果和员工个人利益的角度考虑，所引发的个人所得税问题不容忽视。实务中许多企业在处理股权激励相关的税务问题时，往往缺乏全面的认识和深入的筹划。因此如何结合现行的税收政策进行合理筹划，使激励对象的税收负担最小从而达到最优的激励目标是企业面临的重要课题。本文以福建智行科技信息技术有限公司为例，深入剖析企业实施股权激励的前置税务筹划，从搭建持股平台、股东让渡股权、间接持股是否适用递延纳税政策等多个核心环节展开涉税分析，提出非上市公司股权激励与个人所得税的税收筹划分析。本案例旨在引导学生掌握非上市公司直接股权激励与间接股权激励的税负差异、股权激励相关环节的个人所得税税收筹划，熟悉相关税收优惠政策，进一步激发学生对现行非上市公司股权激励税收法律法规的深入思考和积极探究。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">High-tech enterprises have a high dependence on core talents. To stabilize and maximize the potential of these talents, implementing equity incentives has become an indispensable strategic choice for enterprises to grow and expand. However, from the perspective of both the incentive effect and employees&#39; personal interests, the issue of personal income tax that arises cannot be neglected. In practice, many enterprises often lack comprehensive understanding and thorough planning when dealing with tax issues related to equity incentives. Therefore, how to conduct reasonable planning in accordance with the current tax policies to minimize the tax burden on incentive recipients and achieve optimal incentive goals has become an important issue facing enterprises. Taking Fujian Zhixing Technology Information Co., Ltd. as an example, this article delves into the upfront tax planning for the implementation of equity incentives. It analyzes tax-related issues from various core aspects, such as the establishment of a shareholding platform, the transfer of equity by shareholders, and the applicability of deferred tax policies for indirect shareholding. This case aims to help students grasp the differences in tax burdens between direct and indirect equity incentives in non-listed companies, master the personal income tax planning related to equity incentives, familiarize themselves with relevant tax incentives, and further inspire students to deeply think and actively explore the current tax laws and regulations regarding equity incentives in non-listed companies.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经营管理人员,本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2024</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《税收理论与实务》、《企业税收筹划》、《公司治理》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">非上市公司股权激励的持股方式；大股东让渡股权的个人所得税计算；非上市公司员工股票期权所得的重要时点及征税义务；非上市公司股权激励递延纳税政策</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2024-11</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
